                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I;m assuming you are suing ROZ and Uproar, if not, they will help.
<br />

<br />
First and foremnost get your Cha as igh as possible. Use two opal enrutted steins if need be. Charm with the highest cha possible.
<br />

<br />
Are you rooting your pet on breaks? If not, target your pet and root as soon as it breaks. Mezzing is a longer cast/ WOM iwhout Mes Mastery is chancy. I would go with a root tash remezz. Use a break message andf ask someone in your group to grab aggro by snaring (you ARE getting your pets snared?) or stunning so you can recharm
<br />

<br />
for the future
<br />

<br />
Get eldritch rune. can be cast on the run, instant cast, 1500 hpp rune. When AC breaks have your macro for casting ER ask for a fast heal
<br />

<br />
get lots of defensive AAs Quickbuff, LR5 ID5, Persistent Casting, CHanneling Focus, etc Mes Mastery is great for the extra tick on WOM 
<br />

<br />
May as well haste and weapon the pet, kind of silly to have obe if you aren't getting maxvalue out of it
<br />

<br />

<br />
hope this helped a bit.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Starmist
<br />
&lt;Stone&gt;
