                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Eldrith Rune helps a lot and so does sticking your back into a corner to avoid melee push.
<br />

<br />
Get Pot9/Bot9 whenever you can which has something to do with my next suggestion.  Stand whenever you can.  My general rule is that I'm over 80% mana with a charmed pet, I stand.
<br />

<br />
As far as hasting or duel wielding if you only want to do one...  I'd suggest hasting since you can always slow/dispell it and you won't have to recover your weapons.  You can also us your different haste spells to tailor your pet DPS to suit your comfort level.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
