                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I dont haste or arm pets in Hard LDoN and their damage is just fine
<br />

<br />
in normal LDoN I do but I have good gear and great AA
<br />

<br />

<br />
I dont personally recommend making your pet into something you cant handle  (ie hasted and dualwielding)
<br />

<br />

<br />
one tip I can offer is use NDT on the pet
<br />

<br />
serves 2 purposes
<br />

<br />
1. its obvious that the scarecrow mob is your pet
<br />
2. pet will proc lifetap (cast) - this is helpful when charm breaks cuz it gives you time to recharm if pet is casting on you</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=81508" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Nadia Nightengale</a> 65 Enchantress
