                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just to say - ER has saved my paper ass more times than I can count. Highly recommend it.
<br />

<br />
FWIW, I don't usually give weaps to a charm pet, and seldom haste. But then, my usual group has plenty DPS so we're not all that worried about it.
<br />

<br />
If you're getting mashed frequently then the suggestion of a lower level haste is a good one, or go with none. Those pets do plenty of damage, I can't really see where it's going to make a ton of difference; you can always go with more haste as your equipment improves and breaks get more survivable  <img src="images/smiles/icon_mrgreen.gif" alt="icon_mrgreen.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />--
