                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Things that helped me to maintain hasted charmed pets in LDoN Normal dungeon.
<br />

<br />
1. Faster healer (either main healer or secondary): Whenever you get a good healer, it's a nice bonus but something we can't depend on.
<br />
2. aa's (ER3 & LR5)
<br />
3. mana savers (MP IV & SCM): I used to run out of mana before. I know my equipment is crappy.
<br />
4. HP gears ... I still needs tons more.
<br />

<br />
For me, LR5 and ER3 made a big difference. I can maintain (non-hasted) charmed pet in Hard LDoN without much problem either.
<br />

<br />
As for GoD pets, I am having less success (caused wipe once, killed half the group on the other but I survived) but I can't give it up yet as the potential is HUGE.
<br />

<br />
Best of luck to you as it will only get better.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=664034" target="_blank" class="postlink">Primer</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
