                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As others have said already it does depend on how much the rest of the group helps out on a charm break as to how far to buff your pet - sometimes you will get chain stunned or interrupted through no fault of your own, and the shaman may be busy healing the tank. Try asking the bard to make a hotkey to assist you and mez. 
