Just wanted to say that even an unhasted normal LDON charmed pet is still respectable damage, while being easy to control.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=308116" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ceranai</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
